外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"48b125c2980bbcaeb9ea4aa55b054728c995de89","tid":1577714,"uid":319969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52d2a13333996b566878bfb8204cf0eb4c36edf4","tid":1577714,"uid":161243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"我家爬蟲話:<br />\nmealworm雀街100蚊一斤。唔好睇又唔好食。但毫無殺傷力;<br />\nDubia roach 大約5毫一隻;跑得慢;<br />\n紅蟑廿蚊一杯跑得好快,好難捉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後,玩蟲結果係D蟲比你玩死晒。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"之前我男朋友買咗紅蟑喂守宮<br />\n點知放得唔好<br />\n有幾隻走咗佬<br />\n搞咗勁耐都捉唔囇<br />\n有一日佢老母磅重<br />\n一拎起個磅㩒掣<br />\n成廿隻bb喺度<br />\n佢尖叫咗幾耐<br />\n一路拎拖鞋打我男朋友一路叫佢執走佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死<br />\n<br />\n如果掉幾粒蛋俾佢地唔知會點<br />\n一粒蛋生到十幾隻bb"},{"pid":"bb66dd59653cbc4a2f49bdddc3ac0a1647b51c36","tid":1577714,"uid":206176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"如果將曱甴屋d餌倒出黎<br />\n再半夜灑入狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e978b4106eeeaa00907cba055c287524b5d1b0","tid":1577714,"uid":128569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb66dd59653cbc4a2f49bdddc3ac0a1647b51c36","tid":1577714,"uid":206176,"like":1,